  "slug": "immersive-aircraft",
  "title": "Immersive Aircraft",
  "description": "A bunch of rustic aircraft to travel, transport, and explore!",
  "body": "<h1>Immersive Aircraft</h1>\n\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-aircraft\">\n<img alt=\"Modrinth\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Modrinth-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth&logoColor=000000&color=00AF5C\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/immersive-aircraft\">\n<img alt=\"CurseForge\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/CurseForge-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge&logoColor=000000&color=F16436\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/agxcvAdj2a\">\n<img alt=\"Discord\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Discord-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=discord&logoColor=000000&color=5865F2\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Luke100000/ImmersiveAircraft\">\n<img alt=\"Github\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Github-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=github&color=181717\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://crowdin.com/project/immersive-collection\">\n<img alt=\"Translate via Crowdin\"\nsrc=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Crowdin-NA?style=for-the-badge&logo=crowdin&color=2E3340\">\n</a>\n</p>\n\n<p>\nThis mod adds a bunch of rustic aircraft to travel, transport, and explore!\nThe aircraft have a strong focus on being vanilla-faithful with many details and functionalities, without being\noverly complicated.\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p><img src=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/mcr/atlas?minecraft_version=1.20.1&locations=_immersive_aircraft%3Aaircraft&dependencies=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FLuke100000%2FImmersiveAircraft%2Ftree%2F1.20.1%3F%26c%3D1&resolution=48&background=fancy&row_size=10\" alt=\"Generated Atlas Image\"/></p>\n\n<p>Oh and look, multiplayer compatible!</p>\n\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-aircraft/screenshots/screen1.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<h1>Biplane</h1>\n<p>Let's start with the classic biplane. Fast, one seat, medium difficulty.</p>\n\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-aircraft/screenshots/biplane.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<h1>Airship</h1>\n<p>Slower, but with two seats. Quite easy to maneuver, with acceptable speed thanks to the engine in the back. Also\ncomes in a bulkier cargo variant!</p>\n\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-aircraft/screenshots/airship.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<h1>Gyrodyne</h1>\n<p>Human-powered primitive dual-seater. Trusty, yet neither the fastest nor the easiest to fly. Needs a good initial\npush to get the rotor spinning.</p>\n\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-aircraft/screenshots/gyrodyne.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<h1>Quadrocopter</h1>\n<p>A masterwork of engineering! Four propellers strapped on a bunch of bamboos. It's quite handy for building.</p>\n\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-aircraft/screenshots/quadrocopter.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<h1>Warship</h1>\n<p>\nA beast of copper and steel, built to conquer the skies!\nFour seats, moving turret, 6 weapon mounts and bigger than Minecraft physics would like it to be.\n</p>\n\n<img width=\"872\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=872,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-aircraft/screenshots/warship.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<h1>Some Items to Tinker</h1>\n<p>Since aircraft are generally more complex than, e.g., a boat, a handful of items have been added to make crafting\naircraft feel more like actually assembling something.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p><img src=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/mcr/recipes?minecraft_version=1.20.1&locations=immersive_aircraft%3A.%2A&dependencies=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FLuke100000%2FImmersiveAircraft%2Ftree%2F1.20.1%3F%26c%3D1&resolution=16&animated=False&row_width=835\" alt=\"Generated Recipes Image\"/></p>\n\n<h1>Inventory</h1>\n<p>Upgrade slots, fuel, banner, dye, rocket booster, and storage. Give an aircraft your personal look!</p>\n\n<img width=\"550\"\nsrc=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/cdn-cgi/image/fit=scale-down,w=550,f=jpeg,q=90/https://cdn.conczin.net/immersive-aircraft/screenshots/inventory.jpg\"\nalt=\"Screenshot\"/>\n\n<h1>Many Upgrades</h1>\n<p>Upgrade and tune your aircraft to your liking!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p><img src=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/mcr/atlas?minecraft_version=1.20.1&locations=_immersive_aircraft%3Aupgrades&dependencies=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FLuke100000%2FImmersiveAircraft%2Ftree%2F1.20.1%3F%26c%3D1&resolution=48&background=fancy&row_size=10\" alt=\"Generated Atlas Image\"/></p>\n\n<p>Mount various weapons and utilities to your aircraft!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p><img src=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/mcr/atlas?minecraft_version=1.20.1&locations=_immersive_aircraft%3Aweapons&dependencies=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FLuke100000%2FImmersiveAircraft%2Ftree%2F1.20.1%3F%26c%3D1&resolution=48&background=fancy&row_size=10\" alt=\"Generated Atlas Image\"/></p>\n\n<h1>Video</h1>\n<iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/-XOlaZHOu4I?wmode=transparent\"\nheight=\"480\" width=\"872\"></iframe>\n\n<h1>Addons</h1>\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/man-of-many-planes\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Man%20of%20Many%20Planes&description=A%20set%20of%20additional%20aircraft%20for%20Immersive%20Aircraft%20with%20Create%20support%20in%20mind.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/man-of-many-planes/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Man of Many Planes\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-machinery\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Machinery&description=A%20bunch%20of%20rustic%20machinery%20to%20transport%2C%20mine%2C%20and%20automate%20things.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-machinery/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Machinery\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/aviator-dreams\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Aviator%20Dreams&description=Real%20life%20planes%20from%20small%20to%20big.&icon_url=https%3A//media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/1100/961/64/64/638648594348458560.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Aviator Dreams\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/ia-remaining-airborne\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Remaining%20Airborne&description=A%20set%20of%20classic%20fighters.&icon_url=https%3A//media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/1168/829/64/64/638739800864929977.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Remaining Airborne\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/warfare-wings\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Warfare%20Wings&description=Adds%20many%20WWII%20fighters%20in%20different%20paint%20designs.&icon_url=https%3A//media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/1225/83/64/64/638802892619093611.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Warfare Wings\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/ia_engines\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Better%20Engines&description=Adds%20a%20lot%20of%20new%20upgrades%2C%20mostly%20engines%2C%20but%20also%20a%20turbocharger%20and%20a%20supercharger.&icon_url=https%3A//raw.githubusercontent.com/legoaggelos/ia_engines/refs/heads/main/common/src/main/resources/assets/more_engines/textures/item/supercharger.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Better Engines\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/civilian-aviation\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Civilian%20Aviation&description=Featuring%20stylised%20real%20life%20planes%20and%20helicopters%20from%20all%20eras%21&icon_url=https%3A//media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/1808/958/256/256/639144393942056440.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Civilian Aviation\"/>\n</a></p>\n\n<h1>Resource Packs</h1>\n<p>You don't like my style and/or want better Create integration? Check out these awesome packs here!</p>\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/more-immersive-aircraft\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=More%20Immersive%20Aircraft&description=Vanilla%20friendly%20and%20more%20realistic%20textures%20for%20Immersive%20Aircraft.&icon_url=https%3A//media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/1180/610/64/64/638753853503436917.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"More Immersive Aircraft\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/create-immersive-aircrafts-resource-pack\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Create%20Immersive%20Aircraft&description=Create-styled%20Immersive%20Aircraft%20resource-%20and%20datapack.&icon_url=https%3A//media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/849/496/64/64/638250478085753003.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Create Immersive Aircraft\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/create-style-modded-compats\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Create%20Style%20Compats&description=Item%20textures%20in%20Create%20style.&icon_url=https%3A//media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/485/413/64/64/637785634308178232.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Create Style Compats\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/faithful-32x-immersive-aircraft\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Faithful%20-%20Immersive%20Aircrafts&description=FAITHFUL%2032x%20resource%20pack%20for%20Immersive%20Aircraft.&icon_url=https%3A//media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/798/431/64/64/638160303843226902.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Faithful - Immersive Aircrafts\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/create-immersive-aircraft-warship\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Create%20IA%3A%20Warship&description=Create-styled%20textures%20for%20the%20Warship.&icon_url=https%3A//media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/1004/277/64/64/638525212330806757.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Create IA: Warship\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/create-immersive-aircrafts-andesite-chests-compat\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Create%20Andesite%20Chests&description=Create-styled%20andesite%20chests%20for%20all%20aircraft.&icon_url=https%3A//media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/1010/406/64/64/638534030337746940.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Create Andesite Chests\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/danceboys-biplane-to-xwing\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Danceboys%20X-wing&description=Replaces%20the%20biplane%20with%20an%20x-wing%21&icon_url=https%3A//media.forgecdn.net/avatars/thumbnails/1327/379/64/64/638862867702387346.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Danceboys X-wing\"/>\n</a></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<h1>Immersive Collection</h1>\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-armors\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Armors&description=A%20lot%20of%20unique%20and%20vanilla-faithful%20armor%20sets.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-armors/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Armors\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-aircraft\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Aircraft&description=A%20bunch%20of%20rustic%20aircraft%20to%20travel%2C%20transport%2C%20and%20explore%21&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-aircraft/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Aircraft\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-melodies\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Melodies&description=Play%20custom%20melodies%20on%20various%20instruments%20and%20annoy%20your%20friends%21&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-melodies/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Melodies\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-paintings\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Paintings&description=Drag%20and%20drop%2C%20pixelate%20and%20hang%20up%20beautiful%20art.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-paintings/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Paintings\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-optimization\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Optimization&description=A%20lightweight%20entity-tick-scheduler%20for%20doubling%20your%20TPS.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-optimization/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Optimization\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/selectivebounds\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=SelectiveBounds&description=Hides%20the%20ugly%20block%20selection%20outline%20when%20not%20relevant.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/selectivebounds/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"SelectiveBounds\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-furniture\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Furniture&description=Create%20custom%20and%20fancy%20furniture%20in-game%20or%20choose%20from%20a%20vast%20online%20library.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-furniture/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Furniture\"/>\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/immersive-gateways\">\n<img width=\"275\"\nsrc=\"https://api-rk.conczin.net/embed?title=Immersive%20Gateways&description=Mysterious%2C%20long-forgotten%20portals%20scattered%20across%20the%20Overworld.&icon_url=https%3A//cdn.conczin.net/immersive-gateways/icon.png&width=275&height=100&background_color=16181c\"\nalt=\"Immersive Gateways\"/>\n</a></p>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.conczin.net/common/pixel.png?immersive_pages_hash=b385a88157b140101b9936c1a3266cfb\" alt=\"The page hash for easier page deployment.\"/>",
